    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        How a Decades-Old Loophole Lets Billionaires Avoid Medicare Taxes
    </h1>

    <h2 class="opener__dek " style="display: none" >        Some of Wall Street’s richest and most powerful figures are using a legal loophole to avoid paying millions of dollars in taxes earmarked for health care, a ProPublica investigation found.
    </h2>
    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
