    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/the-secret-irs-files">The Secret IRS Files</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/billionaires-net-investment-income-tax">
                                    How Billionaires Have Sidestepped a Tax Aimed at the Rich
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Wall Street financiers were a clear target of the tax, but some, on questionable legal grounds, have claimed their outsized profits were exempt, sometimes avoiding hundreds of millions in taxes.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/paul-kiel">Paul Kiel</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-12-18EST06:00">Dec. 18, 6 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    

                    
                    
    
        <div class="lead-art">
            <a class="aspect-3-2" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/endo-settlement-opioids-justice-department">
                <img
                    alt=""
